snippet.title: The Magic of Scheherazade - NES (1987)
snippet.description:
Edit: Wow, this got copyright slammed. 3 claims and it's only been up for 10 minutes. 

This really went under the radar back then and has since been considered a hidden gem. Thankfully, the resale market didn't absolutely murder this game's availability as it's still sort of under the radar for legacy owners who might thiink it's just a toss-in. Plus, even if it does make it to resale, it can be had for a decent price. No part of this game is great, but it adds so many little things together for a game that's better than the sum of its parts.
